info.name: Kalan Pacha Milagai Peratal
info.description: A flavorful and spicy South Indian dish made with tender pieces of kalan (mushrooms) and pacha milagai (green chilies), cooked in a rich blend of aromatic spices. The dish is stir-fried to perfection, giving it a tantalizingly spicy and savory taste that’s sure to excite your taste buds. A perfect combination of heat and flavor, it’s a must-try for those who enjoy bold, spicy curries.

info.name: Boiled Egg Chicken Noodles
info.description: A flavorful dish that combines tender chicken pieces, perfectly boiled eggs, and stir-fried noodles, all tossed in a savory sauce. With a delicious mix of textures and a subtle blend of spices, this comforting dish is packed with protein and is sure to satisfy your cravings for a filling, tasty meal.

info.name: Boiled Egg Schezwan Chicken Noodles
info.description: A bold and flavorful dish featuring tender chicken, perfectly boiled eggs, and stir-fried noodles, all tossed in a spicy, tangy Schezwan sauce. The fiery kick of the sauce blends perfectly with the savory chicken and soft noodles, creating a satisfying meal full of heat and flavor.

info.name: Boiled Egg Chicken Fried Rice
info.description: Tender pieces of chicken, perfectly boiled eggs, and freshly cooked rice are stir-fried together with a medley of vegetables and aromatic spices. info.name: Boiled Egg Schezwan Chicken Fried Rice
